===========

Why did Transformers replace LSTMs in modern NLP?

LSTMs process words one by one, making them slower and less effective for long sentences.

Transformers process all words in parallel using Self-Attention, making them faster, more scalable, 
and better at capturing long-range relationships. 

This is why models like BERT, GPT, and ChatGPT are based on the Transformer architecture.

